ke":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63ffe0c5d8169f007f3c073532cbab1079b025a9","tid":1947110,"uid":195380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2980dbb036b012e719389b59768bdf948bdf1b2e","tid":1947110,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:35:56.000Z","msg":"段野點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好問點解淨係得單人相"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:05:24.000Z","msg":"なぜ&mdash;點解<br />\n<br />\nしか.....ない 只有<br />\n<br />\n一人寫真....獨照<br />\n<br />\n後面個聞かないてください⋯⋯請沒有聽過咁解？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:09:33.000Z","msg":"請唔好問。。。咁解"},{"pid":"a7b47c446b52a829fb3fc4c94d261c901dd1334a","tid":1947110,"uid":209603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"480ce920f6a6aff2d5a4a2405752e1dc7ab4a8e1","tid":1947110,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tQ02wby.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtQ02wby.png&h=becc17cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有句話說「胖子都是潛力股」！日本京都大學一位學霸，日前在網路上分享他4年前剛入學和現在的畢業照對比圖，變化之大驚呆一大票網友，「用腦真的會消耗脂肪啊」、「念法律系的都會魔法」？<br />\n <br />\n畢業於全球百大的京都大學谷口柊彌「@Shu8__603」於24日PO上一組對比照，一張是他剛考進京大法律系時，外表完全就是一個普通到不行的肥宅，臉型、體型都很圓潤，且還帶著書呆子眼鏡，走在路上回頭率根本是0。<br />\n <br />\n4年後他站在同一個地方拍照，但照片中的人卻從普男搖身一變成花美男，不但整個人瘦身成功也畫了淡妝，頭髮乾淨俐落梳著現今最潮的髮型，身上穿著合身的名牌西裝套裝，甚至還戴了耳環做裝飾。谷口柊彌PO出照片時也不忘自嘲，「把人性和脂肪當作代價，換來學歷和法律知識」。<br />\n <br />\n貼文一發許多網友也震驚表示「確定是同一個人？」、「用腦竟然會消耗成這樣」、「根本不是整形，是轉世」。不過也有許多眼尖網友指出，「同一個背景，4年後卻整個歪掉？」更大酸「這4年應該是學修圖吧」。谷口柊彌在隨後也po出許多日常生活照來反擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/K5nnhGV0zL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FK5nnhGV0zL&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq%2FUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=7db066a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/K5nnhGV0zL</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"樓主借個位黎置頂可以嗎<br />\n<br />\n要人要錢要資源！線下文宣全港大行動 重建文宣網絡<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ausnGEU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ausnGEU</a>"},{"pid":"e4ed01b49c95ae0fb1e4dce9b3c251651b0bcfed","tid":1947110,"uid":58931,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都叫花美男.. 我樓下個看更都靚仔過佢"},{"pid":"6432ae582d56ba626086e606c969c481e695ce2b","tid":1947110,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"日系嚟講都算樣衰"},{"pid":"01e650d736f5ecaadbc8ef7fcd376643d1a3aa35","tid":1947110,"uid":118886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4ed01b49c95ae0fb1e4dce9b3c251651b0bcfed","tid":1947110,"uid":58931,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都叫花美男.. 我樓下個看更都靚仔過佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:19:43.000Z","msg":"磨牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e900f3606760be698e4006529209f5e8afa02654","tid":1947110,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"佢自己都認P圖失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v5w1Nr3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv5w1Nr3.png&h=cc8a6e70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d89cdf9a9cf2e7acd91440ca83b93160e96ec75","tid":1947110,"uid":181940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"P到個景都扭曲曬"}]}